description: Deletes a fleet. Before you delete a fleet, all vehicles must be dissociated from the fleet. For more information, see Delete a fleet (AWS CLI) in the Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise Developer Guide.

parameters.name: fleetId
parameters.description: The ID of the fleet to delete.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the deleted fleet.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the deleted fleet.
